on the death railway in Burma.

527
00:22:36.405 --> 00:22:37.925
How appalling.

528
00:22:38.325 --> 00:22:39.525
When he got back.

529
00:22:39.925 --> 00:22:41.605
his nerves were... (INHALES)

530
00:22:42.965 --> 00:22:45.205
