538
00:23:06.005 --> 00:23:08.085
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACH)
(FAiNTLY) What are you suggesting?

539
00:23:08.245 --> 00:23:10.085
Closing my eyes?
No. sir.

540
00:23:10.485 --> 00:23:12.085
Oh.
(CLEARS THROAT)

541
00:23:12.245 --> 00:23:13.525
Colonel de Luce. sir.

542
00:23:13.925 --> 00:23:16.565
