902
00:39:10.565 --> 00:39:12.165
Harriet's dressing room.

903
00:39:12.325 --> 00:39:14.565
Sealed up when she left us.

904
00:39:15.445 --> 00:39:19.205
'In eight years. not one of us
has dared to try and open it.'

905
00:39:20.085 --> 00:39:22.405
(WIND CHIMES TINKLING)
