Oh. well done. Flavia!

908
00:39:38.085 --> 00:39:39.845
Now. potassium?

909
00:39:40.645 --> 00:39:40.965
in

910
00:39:41.205 --> 00:39:43.525
Well done. you clever girl!

911
00:39:44.325 --> 00:39:46.405
