"In honour of baby Flavia.

922
00:40:18.565 --> 00:40:20.165
our newest fledgling...

923
00:40:20.485 --> 00:40:22.725
From your friends in The Nest."

924
00:40:23.845 --> 00:40:25.525
'In The Nest?'

925
00:40:26.645 --> 00:40:28.645
(CURIOUS MUSIC)

926
00:40:33.125 --> 00:40:35.445
(CLOCK CHIMES ONE)
(MUSIC FADES)

927
00:40:35.605 --> 00:40:37.445
(TICKING)
FATHER (ECHOES): I alwayS Say.

928
00:40:37.605 --> 00:40:40.165
better three hours too early
than a minute too late.

929
00:40:41.125 --> 00:40:43.125
Father would never
let a clock run slow.

930
00:40:43.205 --> 00:40:44.645
