949
00:41:37.685 --> 00:41:39.845
(ECHOES) What are you going to do
with that? Bash me over the head?

950
00:41:40.245 --> 00:41:42.005
(ECHOES)
You are a vile. despicable..

951
00:41:42.165 --> 00:41:43.685
Don't push me.

952
00:41:44.005 --> 00:41:45.765
(WHISPER ECHOES) CrikerS!

953
