960
00:42:10.325 --> 00:42:11.605
Hello. miss.

961
00:42:11.925 --> 00:42:14.085
You lost your kitten? (CHuCKLES)

962
00:42:14.165 --> 00:42:16.245
My name is Flavia Sabine de Luce.

963
00:42:16.325 --> 00:42:18.485
and I'm here to confess to a murder.

964
00:42:19.285 --> 00:42:21.285
(AWKWARD NOTE. MUSIC STOPS)

965
00:42:21.605 --> 00:42:23.285
It's quite simple. Inspector.

966
00:42:23.445 --> 00:42:26.805
I heard a noise in the garden.
and I went out to investigate.

967
00:42:26.965 --> 00:42:29.365
And someone jumped out at me
from the shadows and-

968
00:42:29.445 --> 00:42:31.125
The shadows? Where exactly?

969
00:42:32.005 --> 00:42:33.525
Behind the potting shed.

970
00:42:33.845 --> 00:42:36.165
I was struggling to get free.

971
00:42:36.325 --> 00:42:39.045
when there was a sudden
gurgle in his throat. like...

972
00:42:40.485 --> 00:42:43.845
..like a man suffering
a myocardial infarction.

973
00:42:43.925 --> 00:42:45.605
A what?

974
00:42:45.685 --> 00:42:46.965
A heart attack.

975
00:42:47.045 --> 00:42:49.445
So. how long were you struggling

976
00:42:49.525 --> 00:42:52.005
with this sickly. dying man

977
00:42:52.165 --> 00:42:54.405
before you realised
you'd murdered him?

978
00:42:54.805 --> 00:42:55.845
(DISTANT PHONE RINGING)

979
00:42:55.925 --> 00:42:58.085
(SIGHS)

980
00:42:58.165 --> 00:42:59.845
I'm listening.

981
00:43:01.925 --> 00:43:04.725
I'm not telling you another thing
until I speak to Father.

982
00:43:05.045 --> 00:43:07.285
That's out of the question.

983
00:43:09.205 --> 00:43:11.685
Look. Inspector.
why don't we make a deal?

984
00:43:11.765 --> 00:43:13.045
