(COUGHS)

1798
01:19:15.925 --> 01:19:17.205
Gah! What the..?
(CAR DOOR OPENS)

1799
01:19:17.605 --> 01:19:19.685
(PANTING)
(CAR DOOR CLOSES. FOOTSTEPS OVERI

1800
01:19:19.845 --> 01:19:21.845
