1847
01:21:09.525 --> 01:21:11.045
Oh! Well
(CHUCKLES)

1848
01:21:11.205 --> 01:21:13.285
Perhaps you'd care to join us.
Detective Sergeant?

1849
01:21:13.365 --> 01:21:14.885
Uh. sir?

1850
