1853
01:21:23.365 --> 01:21:25.845
In through the splenius capitis.

1854
01:21:25.925 --> 01:21:28.485
punctured the atlantoaxial ligament.

1855
01:21:28.885 --> 01:21:31.765
and then slide the needle over the...

1856
